headline.main: Apartment in US President's Trump Tower Rented Out on Airbnb
headline.print_headline: Apartment in US President's Trump Tower Rented Out on Airbnb

lead_paragraph: A Trump Tower apartment rented out on Airbnb had gotten rave reviews before the listing was taken down last week.
